name: Deviritual Candoll
desc: You can reveal 1 Ritual Spell in your hand; Special Summon both this card from your hand and 1 "Deviritual" monster from your Deck, "except "Deviritual Candoll". If this card is Special Summoned from the Deck: You can add 1 Ritual Spell from your Deck to your hand. You can only use each effect of "Deviritual Candoll" once per turn. You cannot Special Summon monsters from the Extra Deck.
